  <summary date="2018-06-27T20:43:54Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Promoting Women in the Aviation Workforce Act

This bill directs the Federal Aviation Administration to create and facilitate the Women in Aviation Advisory Board to promote organizations and programs that provide education, training, mentorship, outreach, and recruitment of women into the aviation industry.</summary>
